{"tid":1722732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"捐血呀!!!","createTime":"2019-11-15T03:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T13:32:37.000Z","uid":62746,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3a5a81f3dea6cde0cb03771f6b173d5670d2d60c","tid":1722732,"uid":62746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"[[[ 請廣傳 ]]]<br />\n血庫血存量就短缺🙏🏻<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>求大家捐血</strong></span>🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n1. 旺角捐血站<br />\n地址:&nbsp;旺角彌敦道580號A周大福商業中心15樓<br />\n(油麻地港鐵站 A2 出口&nbsp;或&nbsp;旺角港鐵站 E2 出口)<br />\n電話: 2770 5930<br />\n前往方法: 從登打士街入口進入「潮流特區」商場，乘電梯上15 字樓<br />\n開放時間:<br />\n星期一至星期六 上午十一時至晚上九時卅分<br />\n星期日及公眾假期&nbsp;上午十一時至下午七時<br />\n<br />\n2. 觀塘捐血站<br />\n地址: 觀塘觀塘道418號創紀之城5期23樓2301室及2316室 (觀塘港鐵站A2出口)<br />\n電話: 3148 1375<br />\n開放時間:<br />\n星期一至星期日及公眾假期: 上午十一時至晚上八時<br />\n<br />\n3. 荃灣捐血站<br />\n地址:&nbsp;荃灣大河道8號<br />\n開放時間:<br />\n星期一至星期日及公眾假期: 上午十一時至晚上八時<br />\n<br />\n4. 元朗捐血站<br />\n地址: 元朗青山公路(元朗段)115-127號開心廣場7樓704-705室<br />\n電話: 2478 6000<br />\n開放時間:<br />\n星期一至星期六: 上午十一時至晚上七時<br />\n星期日及公眾假期: 上午十一時至晚上七時<br />\n<br />\n5. 沙田捐血站<br />\n地址: 沙田正街1號A，香港紅十字會白普理沙田中心一樓<br />\n電話: 2603 0100<br />\n開放時間:<br />\n星期一至星期六&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;上午十一時至下午七時&nbsp;<br />\n星期日及公眾假期&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;上午十一時至下午七時<br />\n<br />\n6. 其他捐血站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticle.asp?bid=85&amp;MenuID=5#.Xc4Fr3DmgwA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww5.ha.org.hk%2Frcbts%2Fhkarticle.asp%3Fbid%3D85%26MenuID%3D5%23.Xc4Fr3DmgwA&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=038672c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticle.asp?bid=85&amp;MenuID=5#.Xc4Fr3DmgwA</a><br />\n總有一個喺你左近!<br />\n<br />\n7. 流動捐血車<br />\n唔知幾時同邊度有, 麻煩自己打上去Red Cross問<br />\n<br />\n去之前可以打去紅十字會諮詢熱線問一問佢地有無開之類， <span style=\"color: pink;\">以免食白果</span>: 2710 1234<br />\n<br />\n基本捐血條件 如下:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticlelistview.asp?nid=41&amp;bid=49&amp;sid=0&amp;MenuID=3#.Xc4HenDmgwA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww5.ha.org.hk%2Frcbts%2Fhkarticlelistview.asp%3Fnid%3D41%26bid%3D49%26sid%3D0%26MenuID%3D3%23.Xc4HenDmgwA&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=3b3ec01a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticlelistview.asp?nid=41&amp;bid=49&amp;sid=0&amp;MenuID=3#.Xc4HenDmgwA</a><br />\n<br />\n捐血須知 如下:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticlelistview.asp?nid=50&amp;bid=49&amp;sid=0&amp;MenuID=3#.Xc4Ht3DmgwA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww5.ha.org.hk%2Frcbts%2Fhkarticlelistview.asp%3Fnid%3D50%26bid%3D49%26sid%3D0%26MenuID%3D3%23.Xc4Ht3DmgwA&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=7c3980b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/hkarticlelistview.asp?nid=50&amp;bid=49&amp;sid=0&amp;MenuID=3#.Xc4Ht3DmgwA</a><br />\n(當中包括:<br />\nA. 捐血後12小時內多喝飲料以補充失去的水份<br />\nB. 捐血後12小時內避免進行劇烈運動<br />\nC. 捐血後12小時內不宜用捐血的手提取重物或過度用力，以免影響傷口癒合<br />\n等等...<br />\n換言之, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過左12小時後, 又無咩不適之類的話, 就可以用返力同拎返重野</span></strong>)<br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句, 有咩其他疑問就麻煩打上去Red Cross問🙏🏻 同埋最重要: <span style=\"color: gold;\">出街時刻提高警覺, 注意安全, 萬事小心</span>🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家❤"},{"pid":"affa8657d33fc9c80cc44d79155cf83c96fed026","tid":1722732,"uid":221401,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"陣間去！柔弱女子一個幫唔到好多手 唯有捐少少血出去幫受傷嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b13933fe6c25ee0b840ae3df53d5a5b56d6e5f2","tid":1722732,"uid":263367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:09:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e18078ce61caf28e67e527ba754fdd410cb30d0d","tid":1722732,"uid":62746,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"affa8657d33fc9c80cc44d79155cf83c96fed026","tid":1722732,"uid":221401,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"陣間去！柔弱女子一個